-Szii Uln'hyrr <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uthata9er.showPublicProfile?language=EN>thata9er</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/29/02 8:53:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=58.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ?</span><hr size=1> Ok - so please tell me if we should re-think this idea.  We're going with a Druid.  We decided that SOW at lvl 14 is very huge for a wiz at lvl 14 and the damage a druid can do with snare and so on at lvl 14 will be very good.  We decided that malee isn't going to be a huge factor in killing other players.  Granted we understand that at times we will face people that will have high resists and in that case we are introuble.  <br>
<br>
However i think with a lvl 20 druid and a lvl 20 Wiz - the damage and the utility things like snare , tracking , sow, heal will be huge.  So what do you think?  <br>
<br>
Also are Druids fear'd at all in PvP?     Keep inmind we might never get past lvl 25!  (hard with stupid real life). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uznailvh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Znail vh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/29/02 9:34:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=58.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ?</span><hr size=1> Wizard plus Druid team can deffinitly be very deadly against those with low resists. And even those with good resists will be in trouble if its 2 vs 1. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utinthalastigris.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tinthalas Tigris</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/15/02 2:22:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=58.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ?</span><hr size=1> If you know hot to use Shock of Lightning, I'd reccomend pairing up with a druid, a ranger, a bard or even a chanter.<br>
<br>
The first three give you speed. The first three give you buffs and healing in varying degrees.<br>
<br>
The chanter gives *you* more direct power, and compliments your class well.<br>
<br>
